name: BoundTightWallets
0:
”Alexa, open Bound Tight Wallets”
”Alexa, ask Bound Tight Wallets for shipping policy”
”Alexa, ask Bound Tight Wallets for return policy”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bound tight wallets
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Bound Tight Wallets creates hand crafted from the Worlds finest hardwoods and high quality hardware. Use this skill to ask for shipping policy and return policy. 

Here's how you can open this skill 
"Alexa, open Bound Tight Wallets"

Once inside the skill you can ask 
-What's your return policy
-What's your shipping policy
